This recipe install a tomcat instance, via a warp package

* Install dependencies : aptitude install libapr1-dev libssl-dev
* Download apache tomcat
* Extract apache tomcat
* cd bin, tar xvzf tomcat-native.tar.gz
* cd tomcat-native-1.2.16-src/native
* ./configure --prefix=$HOME/apache-tomcat-8.5.24 --with-apr=/usr/bin/apr-1-config --with-java-home=/usr/lib/jvm/jdk-9.0.1/
* make install
* libs are now installed in tomcat / lib directory
* purge tomcat
** rm -rf bin/tomcat-native-1.2.16-src
** rm -rf work/* webapps/* temp/* logs/*
** chmod a+x bin/
* package tomcat : .warp/packager/warp_directory.sh apache-tomcat-8.5.24 current apache-tomcat-8.5.24 apache-tomcat-8.5.24_`lsb_release -cs`_`arch`.warp `.warp/common/find_dependencies.sh apache-tomcat-8.5.24`
